<br>
1)if haste (all or some) is proportional to level<br>
<br>
2)if attack stats are relative to environment fought in (ie in Zone_03 certain additions/subtractions are made against your hit percentage, dmg, duel wield, double attack)<br>
<br>
3)if haste applies to different classes differently due to the difference in skill caps<br>
<br>
